:

*1. "Ona je popila čašu šampanjca." (She drank a glass of champagne.)

*2. "Njihov venčanje je bilo proslavljeno šampanjcem." (Their wedding was celebrated with champagne.)

*3. "Kupio sam najskuplji šampanjac." (I bought the most expensive champagne.)

*4. "Čestitke su proslavljene šampanjcem." (The congratulations were celebrated with champagne.)

*5. "Poslužili su nam šampanjac." (They served us champagne.)